    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_varvatos_612821",
        "quote": "I loved the MC5 and the Stooges, but also, the British Invasion - the Kinks and the Yardbirds - and then Led Zeppelin, of course. Alice Cooper was one of my favorite bands.",
