    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_varvatos_612797",
        "quote": "I think the record industry has gotten to be more about labels wondering what the new single is rather than labels nurturing artists. It's gotten away from making a full album of music that someone would want to listen to all the way through.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Varvatos",
            "url": "/quotes/john_varvatos_612797"
